  notes:
    - "Wave 681 (it3511): __get__, __set__, __delete__ dict-presence checks for itertools types."
    - "All values false — itertools iterator types implement the iterator protocol but are not descriptors."
    - "No itertools type defines __get__, __set__, or __delete__ in its own __dict__."
    - "itertools.pairwise requires Python >= 3.10."
    - "All 18 itertools iterator types are checked."
    - "All values verified with Python 3.14.4 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-13."
  created_at: "2026-04-13"
error_model: python_exceptions

